{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":666,"text":"I would like to tell you about a project\nwhich I started about 16 years ago."},{"time":7690,"text":"It's about making new forms of life."},{"time":12388,"text":"And these are made of this kind of tube --"},{"time":16000,"text":"electricity tube, we call it in Holland."},{"time":19000,"text":"And we can start a film about that,"},{"time":23000,"text":"and we can see a little bit\nbackwards in time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27731,"text":"(Video) Narrator: Eventually, these beasts\nare going to live in herds on the beaches."},{"time":32000,"text":"Theo Jansen is working hard\non this evolution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":38209,"text":"Theo Jansen: I want to put\nthese forms of life on the beaches."},{"time":44000,"text":"And they should survive over there,"},{"time":47000,"text":"on their own, in the future."},{"time":51000,"text":"Learning to live on their own --"},{"time":54928,"text":"and it'll take couple of more years"},{"time":59579,"text":"to let them walk on their own."}]},{"cues":[{"time":64698,"text":"Narrator: The mechanical beasts\nwill not get their energy from food,"},{"time":68025,"text":"but from the wind."},{"time":70000,"text":"The wind will move feathers on their back,\nwhich will drive their feet."},{"time":73968,"text":"The beast walks sideways\non the wet sand of the beach,"},{"time":77753,"text":"with its nose pointed into the wind."},{"time":81904,"text":"As soon as it walks into\neither the rolling surf or the dry sand,"},{"time":86736,"text":"it stops, and walks\nin the opposite direction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92197,"text":"Evolution has generated many species."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95848,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":109000,"text":"This is the Animaris Currens Ventosa."}]},{"cues":[{"time":112229,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":119026,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":122000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":130770,"text":"TJ: This is a herd, and it is built\naccording to genetic codes."},{"time":137000,"text":"And it is a sort of race,\nand each and every animal is different,"},{"time":141000,"text":"and the winning codes will multiply."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144195,"text":"This is the wave,\ngoing from left to right."},{"time":146973,"text":"You can see this one."},{"time":152416,"text":"Yes, and now it goes from left to right."},{"time":155884,"text":"This is a new generation, a new family,"},{"time":158690,"text":"which is able to store the wind."},{"time":161888,"text":"So, the wings pump up air\nin lemonade bottles,"},{"time":165339,"text":"which are on top of that."},{"time":167213,"text":"And they can use that energy\nin case the wind falls away,"},{"time":173001,"text":"and the tide is coming up,"},{"time":174516,"text":"and there is still a little bit of energy\nto reach the dunes and save their lives,"},{"time":180325,"text":"because they are drowned very easily."}]},{"cues":[{"time":182349,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":187797,"text":"I could show you this animal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":197780,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":200335,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201562,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":206000,"text":"So, the proportion of the tubes in this\nanimal is very important for the walking."},{"time":212466,"text":"There are 11 numbers,\nwhich I call The 11 Holy Numbers."},{"time":216102,"text":"These are the distances of the tubes\nwhich make it walk that way."},{"time":221000,"text":"In fact, it's a new\ninvention of the wheel."},{"time":224429,"text":"It works the same as a wheel."},{"time":226000,"text":"The axis of a wheel\nstays on the same level,"},{"time":229491,"text":"and this hip is staying\non the same level as well."},{"time":233333,"text":"In fact, this is better than a wheel,"},{"time":235527,"text":"because when you try to drive\nyour bicycle on the beach,"},{"time":240000,"text":"you will notice it's very hard to do."},{"time":243776,"text":"And the feet just step over the sand,"},{"time":248689,"text":"and the wheel has to touch every piece\nof the ground in-between."},{"time":253228,"text":"So 5,000 years after\nthe invention of the wheel,"},{"time":257173,"text":"we have a new wheel."},{"time":259141,"text":"I will show you, in the next video --"},{"time":261000,"text":"can you start it, please? --"},{"time":264498,"text":"that very heavy loads can be moved."},{"time":271083,"text":"There's a guy pushing there, behind,"},{"time":274000,"text":"but it can also walk\non the wind very well."},{"time":277000,"text":"It's 3.2 tons."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282416,"text":"This is working on the stored\nwind in the bottles."},{"time":288817,"text":"It has a feeler, where it can\nfeel obstacles and turn around."},{"time":292809,"text":"You see, it's going the other way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":306098,"text":"Can I have the feeler here?"},{"time":313541,"text":"OK. Good."},{"time":317826,"text":"So, they have to survive\nall the dangers of the beach,"},{"time":323307,"text":"and one of the big dangers is the sea."},{"time":325223,"text":"This is the sea."},{"time":327113,"text":"And it must feel the water of the sea."},{"time":330842,"text":"And this is the water feeler,"},{"time":333000,"text":"and what's very important is this tube."},{"time":335693,"text":"It sucks in air normally,"},{"time":340000,"text":"but when it swallows water,\nit feels the resistance of it."},{"time":344809,"text":"So, imagine that the animal\nis walking towards the sea."},{"time":352761,"text":"As soon as it touches the water --"},{"time":355023,"text":"you should hear a sound of running air."}]},{"cues":[{"time":366235,"text":"(Sound of running air)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":367315,"text":"Yes!"},{"time":371627,"text":"So if it doesn't feel,\nit will be drowned, OK?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":382178,"text":"Here we have the brain of the animal."},{"time":385903,"text":"In fact, it is a step counter,\nand it counts the steps."},{"time":390468,"text":"It's a binary step counter."},{"time":392587,"text":"So as soon it has been to the sea,"},{"time":395654,"text":"it changes the pattern\nof zeroes and ones here."},{"time":403291,"text":"And it always knows\nwhere it is on the beach."},{"time":405918,"text":"So it's very simple brain."},{"time":408654,"text":"It says, well, there's the sea,\nthere are dunes, and I'm here."},{"time":412825,"text":"So it's a sort of imagination\nof the simple world of the beach animal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":418793,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":421571,"text":"One of the biggest enemies are the storms."},{"time":429000,"text":"This is a part of the nose\nof the Animaris Percipiere."},{"time":437285,"text":"When the nose of the animal\nis fixed, the whole animal is fixed."},{"time":442745,"text":"So when the storm is coming up,"},{"time":447070,"text":"it drives a pin into the ground."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451483,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":454023,"text":"Audience member: Wow!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":455212,"text":"The nose is fixed,\nthe whole animal is fixed."},{"time":457358,"text":"The wind may turn, but the animal\nwill always turn its nose into the wind."},{"time":464308,"text":"Now, another couple of years, and these\nanimals will survive on their own."},{"time":470277,"text":"I still have to help them a lot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":472500,"text":"Thank you very much, ladies and gentlemen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":474531,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}